ove - your OS, etc.)  The MS-IME is OS specific, so you would have to tell us this information - then we can give you a direct link to download what you need, and instructions to tell you exactly how to use the IME.  <br>
If you want to do japanese input some other way (using J*star, etc) then I'm afraid that I at least, can't help you, since I haven't used any of those programs in a long time.  <br>
So then:<br>
1) are you on an apple (Mac) or a PC?<br>
2) what is your OS? Windows 95? 98? 2000? ME? (I hope not :P) XP?  NT? OS/2?<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :lol --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/laugh.gif ALT=":lol"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Mac OS-X? etc... <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Mamonaku. 11ban sen ni  Panda densha ga mairimasu.  <!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END-->Abunai desu kara, kiiro no sen no uchigawa made osagarikudasai.  </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> </strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
